# =============================================================================
# DEPLOYMENT NOTES
# =============================================================================
#
# 1. Frontend (React) Requirements:
#    - The deploy script automatically exports these values as REACT_APP_* 
#      environment variables during build
#    - No need to create a separate frontend/.env file
#
# 2. Backend (PHP) Requirements:
#    - PHP scripts read directly from this root .env file
#    - Make sure this file is accessible to your PHP environment
#
# 3. To Deploy:
#    - Update this .env file with your values
#    - Run: ~/proton-prediction-market/deploy-to-cpanel.sh
#    - The script handles everything automatically
#
# 4. Network Selection:
#    - For production: Use MAINNET configuration (uncommented above)
#    - For testing: Comment out MAINNET, uncomment TESTNET
#
# 5. Contract Account:
#    - Must match your deployed smart contract on Proton blockchain
#    - Testnet: https://testnet.protonchain.com
#    - Mainnet: https://proton.org
#
# =============================================================================
